{"tid":1616902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反蒙面法與攬炒","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:03:23.000Z","uid":46148,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6dacc94fccff5e51750af516296e3b3a0b1e4d3","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"立反蒙面法會唔會等於攬炒，其實係唔等於架，因為攬炒戰法只係適用於一方想進攻，另一方<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願意犧牲小我</span></span>，老實說和理非到依家都重係和理非，簡單講都係未有覺悟去作出重大犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n老實說佢用緊急法去立反蒙面法其實都只係不停<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試水溫</span>，當立完反蒙面法都重未平息到，就只會不停立更多法或凍結資產等等，雖然不停講end game，其實大家都重覺得有險可守，有美國制裁，等支爆，未去到自己要犧牲嘅時候，但好可惜就算真係支爆，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個軍政府嘅事實都係唔會改變</span></span>，香港人最終都係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同極權決一死戰</span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以我敢講如果立反蒙面法之後和理非怕而退卻的話，前線勇武只會不斷被犧牲，而和理非會不停被打壓，一係成場運動輸香港玩完，一係爆煲反擊，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但當時已經冇左一大班手足</span></span><br />\n預期係咁，不如係更多手足被犧牲前，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家真係同行全民起義</span></span>，立法反蒙面法嘅當日，就係響起香港人起義嘅旗號。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅意志已經傳承左俾我嘅師弟師妹，而佢地都會傳承俾比佢地更年輕嘅下一代，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我深信傳承係人一生嘅意義，我敢說我已經死而無憾。</span><br />\n所以真香港人們，到時你地屋企有獲嘅拎獲，有桶嘅拎桶，一切能用嘅拎出嚟，保護自己，保護手足，保護我地嘅下一代，真香港人你地願意同我，同我地一班前線手足，不分和勇，一齊去同極權搏鬥，留返一個有希望嘅未來俾我地下一代嗎"},{"pid":"e030ab5040e6d1185944ffc08dc9c1d5c05f4a99","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"1/N"},{"pid":"a346236c8645ac2c5ff42a436ea24026165da577","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"2/N"},{"pid":"0be611423f5f497e52d18f3a67ab359bf001a9b5","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"3/N"},{"pid":"5b03fc8bac63d9f2c499d56b701e8d98862dfb7f","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"4/N"},{"pid":"138dffc2e36412ac469eacf2677444dbeae0c256","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"5/N"},{"pid":"e7974a27aeafa600b17606001b3500b4f2874512","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"6/N"},{"pid":"5a4917adc71a86b3db9381499576facb67e976a5","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"7/N"},{"pid":"cf0f7664577182bc145cd4af413123c24c70e84e","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"8/N"},{"pid":"206266fd3d6cf26b8984dc1f772406bb4c0cc2e1","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"9/N"},{"pid":"d6783ddc518251d50d082445d212ab7a510f8adf","tid":1616902,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"10/N"},{"pid":"466a82459bce4f1525dbf502a367a8eddfcb44fd","tid":1616902,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd45173971f6d9fa1d070907d226ce333f572b5","tid":1616902,"uid":321050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"becf98ff7230f49b78a68884162e3b8a030c55cb","tid":1616902,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"前大學教授啱啱又有贈言：不蒙面的超人。蒙面，周身護具，打很多次。不蒙面，卸下護具，只帶兵器，打一次。"},{"pid":"11f41c7c941455509d429475a3103fdfeed109a4","tid":1616902,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:50:10.000Z